Vantage Capital, Africa’s largest mezzanine fund manager, announced today that it has provided $12.5 million of funding to Purple Capital, a prominent Nigerian real estate company and financial service provider. Purple Capital is the developer of the iconic 6,000m² Maryland Mall, a neighbourhood shopping centre in the Ikeja district of Lagos.PURPLE_VANTAGE PRESS RELEASE (final) BECOME A MEMBER   |   MEDIA & NEWS   |   DOWNLOADS +27 11 268 0041 info@savca.co.za © 2018 SAVCA. | Powered By Spheralytical